&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exciting opportunity for the right forward thinking GP to join our dynamic team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JS Medical Practice is looking to recruit Salaried GPs for 4-8 clinical sessions per week.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;JS Medical Practice in Haringey is an established innovation award winning GP practice running from three branch sites.  We have a combined patient population of nearly 13,000 patients.  We are open to new ideas and consistently looking at ways of delivering better services. The Practice is well established and respected locally. We pride ourselves on providing high quality care and innovation in development of local services working closely with our Primary Care Network (PCN).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The practice team has a large and rapidly growing clinical team of GPs, ANPs, Prescribing Pharmacists, Practice Nurses, HCAs and Social Link Prescriber.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Information:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practice population circa 13,000&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High QOF achievers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;“GOOD” CQC rating&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practice uses Emis Web, AccuRx, Emis Document Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practice will be also using e-Consults, Surgery Connect (as of Nov 2020)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Friendly and cohesive existing team with high levels of experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Weekly meeting for all clinical staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;On-site &amp; off-site parking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you feel that you have the qualities and skills to succeed in this exciting role we would love to hear from you!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
